 Functional Overlap Summary

  High overlap — validator sprawl (58 files)

  The biggest redundancy. The DOC-SCRIPT-0989 through DOC-SCRIPT-1025
  series are individually generated validators — one per ID type
  (rule_id, run_id, schema_id, alert_id, etc.). They all do the same
  thing for different ID types. The generator that made them
  (DOC-SCRIPT-ID-GEN-VALIDATORS-992__generate_id_validators.py) still
  exists alongside its outputs.

  Candidates to consolidate: All validate_*_id.py scripts → one
  parameterized validator.

